.\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 263, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"None\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 177}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening day\", \"from\": 196, \"to\": 211}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Golf Tournament\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 242}, {\"ngram\": \"his home country\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 262}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pavon was overcome with emotion on the first tee at Le Golf National, so much so that he said it impacted his play.\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Pavon\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 270}, {\"ngram\": \"emotion\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 296}, {\"ngram\": \"the first tee\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"Le Golf National\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"his play\", \"from\": 371, \"to\": 379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His countryman, Victor Perez, had the honor of hitting the first shot to begin the competition earlier in the day.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 397, \"end\": 409, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.736318292213366e-17, \"text\": \"Victor Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Victor_Perez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His countryman\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"the honor\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"the first shot\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 450}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 475}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat was a crazy moment which I wasn't prepared,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Pavon, 31, who shot 71. \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAt that moment, too big, took emotions, too many people screaming just your name.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 665, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThat\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"a crazy moment\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"Pavon\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 562}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAt\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"emotions\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 622}, {\"ngram\": \"too many people\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"just your name\", \"from\": 650, \"to\": 664}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo it's very special, so yeah, that was something I had to fight a little bit, those emotions, and it was a tough day overall because like the emotions out there, every single shot, every single tee shot, every putt, everybody is pushing you, wants to do great.\", \"from\": 667, \"to\": 931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 719}, {\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 747}, {\"ngram\": \"those emotions\", \"from\": 749, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotions\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 821}, {\"ngram\": \"every single shot\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"every single tee shot\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 873}, {\"ngram\": \"every putt\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 885}, {\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 887, \"to\": 896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So it's tough to manage all of this.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It takes a lot of energy, and I am pretty pleased the way that I did so far today.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Pavon won his first DP World Tour event last fall and then earned a PGA Tour card via a top-10 exemption.\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 1161, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.47515457905297e-16, \"text\": \"PGA Tour\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/PGA_Tour\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/P