: 1475, \"to\": 1480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou do not really have a hole where you can calm down and breathe and take some water.\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cYou\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1493}, {\"ngram\": \"a hole\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1519}, {\"ngram\": \"some water\", \"from\": 1565, \"to\": 1575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's always you get back to that tee box and everyone screaming your name, and stuff like this, so you never get some rest.\", \"from\": 1577, \"to\": 1700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that tee box\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"your name\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1650}, {\"ngram\": \"some rest\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1699}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was a very tiring day for me.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d For Perez, 31, who played college golf at the University of New Mexico and has three DP World Tour wins, the experience was just as nerve-racking.\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1886, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1749, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"score\": 0.9997792717232004, \"rank\": 0.00017983598035366727, \"text\": \"Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very tiring day\", \"from\": 1710, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"me.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1738}, {\"ngram\": \"college golf\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"the University\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1795}, {\"ngram\": \"New Mexico\", \"from\": 1799, \"to\": 1809}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1858}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He hit the first shot of the tournament at 9 a.m. local time.\", \"from\": 1887, \"to\": 1948, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first shot\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"the tournament\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1926}, {\"ngram\": \"9 a.m.\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"local time\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cObviously a lot going on,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Perez, who shot 70. \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt's never the easiest place for a golfer to be.\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 2058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1992, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"score\": 0.9997792717232004, \"rank\": 0.00017983598035366727, \"text\": \"Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cObviously a lot\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1968}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1978, \"to\": 1981}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2012}, {\"ngram\": \"the easiest place\", \"from\": 2021, \"to\": 2038}, {\"ngram\": \"a golfer\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nobody enjoys the 1st tee, I think ever.\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nobody\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1st tee\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2084}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI told myself on the range, I told my caddie, James, let us be there the full 10 minutes before and really soak it in all in.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2229, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"score\": 0.668429510954599, \"rank\": 0.49358232581632283, \"text\": \"James\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/James_VI_and_I\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2105}, {\"ngram\": \"the range\", \"from\": 2121, \"to\": 2130}, {\"ngram\": \"my caddie\", \"from\": 2139, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's definitely a once-in-a-lifetime.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a-lifetime\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will never hit this tee shot again, opening games in Paris and being French and having all the home support.\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2323, \"end\": 2328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9978246086745571, \"rank\": 0.0021801339698025984, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this tee\", \"from\": 2285, \"to\": 2293}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2319}, {\"ngram\": \"all the home support\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to be there.\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2400, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There wasn't going to be more pressure whether I was there 10 minutes or four minutes.\", \"from\": 2401, \"to\": 2487, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more pressure\", \"from\": 2426, \"to\": 2439}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSo I was like, you might as well just try to be there and take it all in and enjoy the people.\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 2575, \"to\": 2585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was great.\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I managed to hit a good shot, actually.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Perez said the experience, in some ways, was more meaningful than getting his first DP World Tour victory in 2019 at the Dunhill Links Championship.\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2793, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2645, \"end\": 2650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"score\": 0.9997792717232004, \"rank\": 0.00017983598035366727, \"text\": \"Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good shot\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2629}, {\"ngram\": \"the experience\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2669}, {\"ngram\": \"some ways\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"his first DP World Tour victory\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"the Dunhill Links Championship\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2791}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis sticks out a little bit more, doing it in France in a place where\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094this used to be a putting green when we were kids,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d he said of where he was standing on the Le Golf National grounds.\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2990, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2845, \"end\": 2851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8455035059519277, \"rank\": 0.10460288723823204, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2802}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 2855, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"a putting green\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2902}, {\"ngram\": \"kids\", \"from\": 2916, \"to\": 2920}, {\"ngram\": \"the Le Golf National grounds\", \"from\": 2961, \"to\": 2989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe played the under-12, under-14, under-16 French Juniors here, and I remember staying in the Novotel (hotel on site) and coming out at 9 o'clock doing putting games against the older guys and trying to win and playing for a Coke or something.\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3088, \"end\": 3095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novotel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Novotel\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novotel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Novotel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cWe\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 2996}, {\"ngram\": \"the under-12\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3016}, {\"ngram\": \"under-14\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3026}, {\"ngram\": \"under-16 French Juniors\", \"from\": 3028, \"to\": 3051}, {\"ngram\": \"(hotel\", \"from\": 3096, \"to\": 3102}, {\"ngram\": \"site\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3110}, {\"ngram\": \"9 o'clock\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3139}, {\"ngram\": \"games\", \"from\": 3154, \"to\": 3159}, {\"ngram\": \"the older guys\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3182}, {\"ngram\": \"a Coke\", \"from\": 3217, \"to\": 3223}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3227, \"to\": 3236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis place is very special for me, and I think Matthieu will agree the same when you guys speak to him in a bit.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3289, \"end\": 3297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M._Pokora\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.684441141823575e-23, \"text\": \"Matthieu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M._Pokora\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/M._Pokora\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis place\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3252}, {\"ngram\": \"you guys\", \"from\": 3323, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 3348, \"to\": 3353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's